                     <seg style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans 25.11.93. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>[...]<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Not relevant to M.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Still in the jungle, and I do not know for how long more. It is so irksome, so dreary. It is only the hope of doing something good that keeps me up. Sir Jo Hooker writes encouragingly. So Mueller does. Still a lonesome life in the jungle comes very heavy.</p>
